其中:
- `Mi`: LoadBlock[i] 开始地址
- `Si`: LoadBlock[i] 实际起始地址
- `Ei`: LoadBlock[i] 结束地址

**二分查找算法**:
```cpp
LoadBlock* findLoadBlock(uint64_t vaddr, bool quick = true) {
    uint64_t clocaddr = vaddr & vabits_mask;
    auto& loads = quick ? mQuickLoad : mLoad;

    // 边界检查优化
    if (clocaddr < loads[0].vaddr() || 
        clocaddr >= loads[n-1].vaddr() + loads[n-1].size()) {
        return nullptr;
    }

    // 二分查找 O(log n)
    int left = 0, right = loads.size() - 1;
    while (left <= right) {
        int mid = (left + right) / 2;
        if (loads[mid].virtualContains(clocaddr)) {
            return &loads[mid];
        }
        if (clocaddr < loads[mid].vaddr()) {
            right = mid - 1;
        } else {
            left = mid + 1;
        }
    }
    return nullptr;
}
```

## 五、虚拟地址管理

### 5.1 地址掩码机制

```cpp
// vabits_mask: 提取有效虚拟地址位
// ARM64: 48位或52位 VA
uint64_t vabits_mask = (1ULL << VA_BITS) - 1;

// pointer_mask: 处理压缩指针
// ART HeapReference: 32位压缩
uint64_t pointer_mask = 0xFFFFFFFF;

// 使用示例
uint64_t normalized_addr = vaddr & vabits_mask;
uint32_t compressed_ref = obj->klass() & pointer_mask;
```

### 5.2 ARM64 特殊处理

**Pointer Authentication Code (PAC)**:
```cpp
// NT_ARM_PAC_MASK 提供 PAC 数据掩码
uint64_t pac_data_mask = 0x007FFFFFFFFFFFFF; // 示例
uint64_t code_pointer = pc & pac_data_mask;
```

**Top Byte Ignore (TBI)**:
- 高 8 位可用于标记
- vabits_mask 自动过滤高字节

## 六、原生内存跟踪

### 6.1 NativeAllocationRegistry 机制

```mermaid
graph LR
    JO[Java Object<br/>Bitmap] 
    CL[sun.misc.Cleaner]
    CT[CleanerThunk]
    NAR[NativeAllocationRegistry]
    NM[Native Memory<br/>Pixel Data]

    CL -->|referent| JO
    CL -->|thunk| CT
    CT -->|this$0| NAR
    NAR -->|size| NM

    style NM fill:#f9f,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
```

**遍历过程**:
1. 收集所有 `sun.misc.Cleaner` 对象
2. 读取 `referent` 字段获取 Java 对象
3. 读取 `thunk.this$0` 获取 NativeAllocationRegistry
4. 读取 `registry.size` 获取原生内存大小
5. 累加到对应 Class 的统计中

**代码实现**:
```cpp
// cmd_top.cpp
for (auto& cleaner : cleaners) {
    Object referent = cleaner.GetReferent();
    CleanerThunk thunk = cleaner.GetThunk();
    NativeAllocationRegistry registry = thunk.GetRegistry();
    uint64_t native_size = registry.GetSize();

    // 关联到 referent 的 Class
    Class klass = referent.GetClass();
    stats[klass].native_size += native_size;
}
```

## 七、线程与同步

### 7.1 Thread 对象布局

```cpp
class Thread {
    ThreadTls32 tls32_;   // 32位字段
    ThreadTlsPtr tlsPtr_; // 指针大小字段
};

struct ThreadTls32 {
    uint32_t state_and_flags;  // 低4位=状态，高位=标志
    uint32_t suspend_count;
    uint32_t tid;              // OS 线程 ID
    // ...
};

struct ThreadTlsPtr {
    void* stack_begin;
    void* stack_end;
    const char* name;
    ManagedStack* managed_stack;  // Java 栈帧
    // ...
};
```

### 7.2 ThreadState 编码

```cpp
enum ThreadState {
    kRunnable = 0,
    kSleeping = 1,
    kBlocked = 2,
    kWaiting = 3,
    kWaitingForGcToComplete = 4,
    kWaitingPerformingGc = 5,
    kWaitingForSignalCatcherOutput = 6,
    // ... 共16种状态
};

// 提取状态
ThreadState state = static_cast<ThreadState>(
    thread.tls32_.state_and_flags & 0x0F
);
```

### 7.3 Monitor 锁字结构

```cpp
union LockWord {
    uint32_t value;
    struct {
        uint32_t state : 2;      // 锁状态
        union {
            uint32_t thin_lock_owner : 16; // Thin lock: ThreadID
            uint32_t hash_state : 30;      // Hash state
            uint32_t* monitor_ptr;         // Fat lock: Monitor*
        };
    };
};
```

## 八、DEX 文件格式

### 8.1 DEX Header

```
+0x00: magic[8]        "dex\n039\0"
+0x08: checksum        (Adler32)
+0x0C: signature[20]   (SHA-1)
+0x20: file_size
+0x24: header_size     (0x70)
+0x28: endian_tag      (0x12345678)
+0x2C: link_size/link_off
+0x34: map_off
+0x38: string_ids_size/string_ids_off
+0x40: type_ids_size/type_ids_off
+0x48: proto_ids_size/proto_ids_off
+0x50: field_ids_size/field_ids_off
+0x58: method_ids_size/method_ids_off
+0x60: class_defs_size/class_defs_off
+0x68: data_size/data_off
```

### 8.2 方法签名解析

```cpp
// ArtMethod → MethodId → ProtoId → TypeList
const char* GetMethodSignature(ArtMethod& method) {
    uint32_t method_idx = method.GetDexMethodIndex();
    DexFile& dex = method.GetDexFile();

    MethodId& method_id = dex.GetMethodId(method_idx);
    const char* name = dex.GetString(method_id.name_idx);

    ProtoId& proto = dex.GetProto(method_id.proto_idx);
    const char* shorty = dex.GetString(proto.shorty_idx);
    TypeList& params = dex.GetTypeList(proto.parameters_off);

    // 构造完整签名: 返回类型 名称(参数...)
    return FormatSignature(proto.return_type_idx, name, params);
}
```

## 九、最佳实践

### 9.1 安全的对象遍历

```cpp
try {
    Android::ForeachObjects([](Object& obj) {
        if (!obj.IsValid()) return true;  // 跳过无效对象
        if (obj.IsClass()) return true;   // 跳过 Class 对象本身

        Class klass = obj.GetClass();
        // 处理对象...
        return true;  // 继续遍历
    }, EACH_APP_OBJECTS | EACH_ZYGOTE_OBJECTS);
} catch (InvalidAddressException& e) {
    LOGW("Heap walking interrupted: %s", e.what());
}
```

### 9.2 性能优化技巧

**使用 QUICK_CACHE 避免重复查找**:
```cpp
DEFINE_QUICK_CACHE(Class, GetClass, klass)
// 自动生成缓存版本的 GetClass()
// 首次调用解析，后续调用返回缓存
```

**复用 LoadBlock 减少查找**:
```cpp
Class klass = obj.GetClass();  // 查找 LoadBlock
String name = klass.GetName(); // 复用 obj 的 LoadBlock
```

### 9.3 版本兼容代码模式

```cpp
if (Android::Sdk() >= __ANDROID_API_W__) {
    // W+ 版本逻辑
    ArtField* fields = clazz.GetFields();
    for (uint32_t i = 0; i < clazz.NumFields(); i++) {
        if (fields[i].IsStatic()) {
            // 处理静态字段
        }
    }
} else {
    // Pre-W 版本逻辑
    ArtField* sfields = clazz.GetSFields();
    for (uint32_t i = 0; i < clazz.NumStaticFields(); i++) {
        // 处理静态字段
    }
}
```

---

